      <section id="details">
        <h2 class="gem-c-heading gem-c-heading--font-size-27 gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  ">Details</h2>


        
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<div class="call-to-action">
<h3 id="update-29-october">Update 29 October</h3>

<p>Following the <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/news/plan-for-jobs-chancellor-increases-financial-support-for-businesses-and-workers#business-grants-1" class="govuk-link">announcement of changes in the support available to businesses</a> in areas with both high and very high COVID alert levels, this guidance is being revised.</p>

<p>We will publish updated guidance for the Local Restrictions Support Grants within the next week.</p>
</div>

<p>This guidance sets out details and eligibility criteria for the Local Restrictions Support Grant (LRSG).</p>

<p>It informs local authorities about the operation and delivery of the funding scheme.</p>

<div class="example">
<p>There is different <a href="https://www.gov.uk/guidance/check-if-youre-eligible-for-the-coronavirus-local-restrictions-support-grant" class="govuk-link">guidance for businesses</a>.</p>
</div>

</div>
</div>

      </section>
    </div>

